rained personnel in a setting equipped and staffed for cardiopulmonary resuscitation.', 'Antagonism', 'The use of naltrexone is considered contraindicated in patients receiving opioids or dependent on opioids, including those maintained on opiate agonists (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/32352/', '', 'Loperamide, Eluxadoline, Diphenoxylate, Difenoxin, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone, Naltrexone', 'Morphine, Nalmefene, Disulfiram, Acamprosate, Lorcaserin, Diethylpropion, Mazindol', 1767369485);
